summary: Grey Matter Art is excited to announce our next @marvel release for the visually captivating movie, "Spider-Man: Into the...
caption:
Grey Matter Art is excited to announce our next @marvel release for the visually captivating movie, “Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse” by artist, Anthony Petrie (@zombiebacons). This has become one of our favorite movies of the year, so we weren’t too surprised it won an Academy Award for the best-animated feature. We are beyond thrilled to see Anthony continue to expand on his Marvel poster series with this 8 color screen print featuring transparent & fluorescent inks with a clear gloss layer! “Spider-Man: Into the Spider-Verse” goes on sale this Thursday, February 28th at 1PM (est) at greymatterart.com! For the full details on the release you can sign up for our newsletter or go to our homepage. #greymatterart #marvel #spiderverse #milesmorales #spiderman #spiderham #spidergwen #spidermannoir #peniparker #marvel #art #print #comic #anthonypetrie
